import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground } from 'docz';
import WidgetTable from '../WidgetTable';
import { columns, data } from './data';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"widgettable"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#widgettable"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`WidgetTable`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#properties"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<WidgetTable columns={columns} data={data} width={600} />`} __scope={{props,WidgetTable,columns,data}}>
  <WidgetTable columns={columns} data={data} width={600} />
</Playground></MDXTag>
